video.title: Jurassic World Camp Cretaceous
video.synopsis: Six teens invited to attend a state-of-the-art adventure camp on Isla Nublar must band together to survive when the dinosaurs break out of captivity.

episodes.synopsis: After waiting his whole life to see dinosaurs, lucky Darius wins the chance to join five other campers on Isla Nublar for a once-in-a-lifetime adventure.
episodes.title: Camp Cretaceous

episodes.synopsis: With the rest of the crew off visiting a genetics lab, Kenji sneaks Darius into the park's top-secret underbelly — and straight into danger.
episodes.title: Secrets

episodes.synopsis: The campers hop into their Gyrospheres to help move a dinosaur herd toward fresh grazing lands. But an incoming storm stirs up unexpected trouble.
episodes.title: The Cattle Drive

episodes.synopsis: Darius remembers the promise he made to his dad. Elsewhere on the island, the campers find themselves face-to-face with a newly freed threat.
episodes.title: Things Fall Apart

episodes.synopsis: After a close encounter with the Indominus, the gang seeks shelter in the genetics lab, where a strange scientist reveals the truth about Dr. Wu.
episodes.title: Happy Birthday, Eddie!

episodes.synopsis: Sammy's secret shocks everyone — but there's no time for anger when an accident unleashes a flock of Pteranodons and forces the crew below ground.
episodes.title: Welcome to Jurassic World

episodes.synopsis: The campers leave the Mosasaurus lagoon and fight their way onto the monorail … where Ben gets a chance to face his fears.
episodes.title: Last Day of Camp

episodes.synopsis: It's a race against time as the campers make their way to the main dock to catch the last ferry leaving the island. But what if they're too late?
episodes.title: End of the Line

episodes.synopsis: Still stranded on the island — and still reeling from the apparent loss of Ben — the campers make a last-ditch attempt at rescue by sending out an SOS.
episodes.title: A Beacon of Hope

episodes.synopsis: Darius and Sammy face a moral dilemma while searching the park for supplies. The campers start building a new treehouse. Brooklynn sees something odd.
episodes.title: The Art of Chill

episodes.synopsis: Brooklynn, Sammy and Yasmina team up to investigate strange noises in the park. Elsewhere, Darius and Kenji go exploring and witness a majestic sight.
episodes.title: The Watering Hole

episodes.synopsis: A bonfire in the distance signals that the campers have company: a pair of posh eco-tourists and their disgruntled security guy. But can they be trusted?
episodes.title: Salvation

episodes.synopsis: The campers reunite with a long-lost friend, who shares an inspiring story — then reveals that Mitch, Tiff and Hap aren't who they seem.
episodes.title: Brave

episodes.synopsis: Darius must make a difficult choice to save Sammy and Yasmina. Meanwhile, the remaining campers are trying to decide if Hap is a friend... or a foe.
episodes.title: Misguided

episodes.synopsis: Brooklynn, Ben, Kenji and Yasmina work to uncover a secret and restore power to the park as Darius leads Mitch and Tiff straight into a T. rex trap.
episodes.title: Step One

episodes.synopsis: A guilty Darius is determined to protect the island's innocent dinos — even if he has to do it all alone. But with luck, maybe he won't have to...
episodes.title: Chaos Theory

episodes.synopsis: The campers catch a lift to Lookout Point in search of materials to make a sail, then must quickly find a way back down. Ben worries about leaving Bumpy.
episodes.title: View from the Top

episodes.synopsis: After finding Mitch and Tiff's abandoned yacht, the happy campers celebrate. But the party's over when something big goes bump in the night.
episodes.title: Safe Harbor

episodes.synopsis: Kenji takes the campers to his father's penthouse to gather supplies — but they've soon got company. Sammy reflects on what life must be like back home.
episodes.title: Casa De Kenji

episodes.synopsis: A thrilling chase brings Darius, Kenji and Yaz to the old Jurassic Park Visitors Center. Elsewhere on the island, Brooklynn and Sammy find a secret lab.
episodes.title: Clever Girl

episodes.synopsis: Sammy and Brooklynn rush to warn the others about a sinister new threat while Darius, unaware of the danger, searches for his dad's favorite dinosaur.
episodes.title: Eye of the Storm

episodes.synopsis: As a poisoned camper fights to survive, it's up to Yaz — the fastest among them — to fetch the antidote before it's too late.
episodes.title: The Long Run

episodes.synopsis: It's crunch time for the campers to get to the boat and make their escape... until Ben disappears, deciding he'd rather stay. Can Darius change his mind?
episodes.title: A Shock to the System

episodes.synopsis: With multiple threats running rampant on the island, dinosaur lover Darius must put his feelings aside and make a difficult decision.
episodes.title: Escape from Isla Nublar

episodes.synopsis: The group is forced to switch gears when a familiar face returns to Isla Nublar. Now, getting off the island is no longer the most important thing.
episodes.title: Whatever It Takes

episodes.synopsis: With Brooklynn being held prisoner, the remaining campers hatch a plan to rescue her — and it won't be easy.
episodes.title: Stay on Mission

episodes.synopsis: Out at sea, the campers see sunny skies... then discover a stowaway on board. A surprise attack from the deep leaves them stranded on unfamiliar shores.
episodes.title: Beneath the Surface

episodes.synopsis: The weary crew dodges danger in the desert while trying to figure out where they are. But they unearth more questions than answers.
episodes.title: At Least...

episodes.synopsis: A strange tunnel takes the teens to a lush forest, where they meet a mysterious scientist studying dino behavior. The question is: Can they trust her?
episodes.title: Turning Dr. Turner

episodes.synopsis: With Dr. Turner's help, the campers hatch a plan to get off the island that finds them crossing a snowy arctic biome — and making a selfless rescue.
episodes.title: Rude Awakening

episodes.synopsis: After learning the truth about Mae's boss, Sammy's ready to go rogue to take him down... just as Mae gets ready to confront him. Cue the killer robots!
episodes.title: The Long Game

episodes.synopsis: With Mae in serious condition and Kash's end game clear, the campers vow to save the dinosaurs and stop Mantah Corp. But evil BRADs are everywhere.
episodes.title: Mission Critical

episodes.synopsis: Darius has to think fast to distract Kash and protect the others, so he pretends to hate dinos as much as Kash does — while learning everything he can.
episodes.title: Staying Alive

episodes.synopsis: Brooklynn must devise a hack to help Darius, who's being tailed by an upgraded BRAD-X. Meanwhile, Kash prepares to woo a group of dangerous investors.
episodes.title: Technical Difficulties

episodes.synopsis: Darius keeps Kash busy with competitive video gaming while the others break into the nursery. Yaz asks Brooklynn how she feels about Kenji.
episodes.title: Dino-Sitting

episodes.synopsis: Ben's refusal to bond with a new friend leads to regret — and a realization that it's time to take Kash down. Kenji and Brooklynn face their feelings.
episodes.title: Taking Control

episodes.synopsis: Just when it feels like things are getting back to normal, Kash's boss arrives on Mantah Corp. island and begins moving forward with a devastating plan.
episodes.title: Who's the Boss?
